    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intro</h2>Master your magic as an Apprentice Mage, in this pixel-art fantasy RPG!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/800ee1305a27ac43a91206385c0db2a6.avif?t=1748235420\" width=256 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Background</h2>A magic apprenticeship only lasts 4 years; can you truly prove you have what it takes to become a Master Mage in such a short time?<br><br><br>Thankfully, you're not alone. Mages like yourself seek out <strong><i>Maegas</i></strong>, colorful creatures composed entirely of magic, to help them learn new types of magic and spells.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/7a3ab591feb616d593185c33565f3677.apng?t=1748235420\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/7a3ab591feb616d593185c33565f3677.poster.avif?t=1748235420\" class=\"bb_img\" width=224 height=128 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Buy and upgrade homes</strong> that you'll be able to customize to your liking!<br>    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/2231cddf2553a291d12e91c91b5d5070.poster.avif?t=1748235420\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/2231cddf2553a291d12e91c91b5d5070.webm?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/2231cddf2553a291d12e91c91b5d5070.mp4?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Use the <i>Maegas</i> you gather in <strong>magical duels</strong> with other mages or magical creatures.<br>     <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/52a21ee39706997020265097230d2c47.poster.avif?t=1748235420\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/52a21ee39706997020265097230d2c47.webm?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/52a21ee39706997020265097230d2c47.mp4?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Make friends and build relationships</strong> with people you meet along the way ~<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/ba46f86fb0daf0f5e08cfaf22254220a.poster.avif?t=1748235420\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/ba46f86fb0daf0f5e08cfaf22254220a.webm?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/ba46f86fb0daf0f5e08cfaf22254220a.mp4?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Craft powerful magical items and useful potions</strong> to help on your journey to become a Master Mage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/589be02cea71068424ebc7d57d206e64.poster.avif?t=1748235420\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858410/extras/589be02cea71068424ebc7d57d206e64.webm?t=1748235420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https